{
  "version": 1,
  "_doc": "Single source of truth for ECA channel ids, human-readable labels, and the capability→channel mapping consumed by both the JS frontend (Blockly dropdowns, LLM catalog, sensor panel) and the Python bridge (OSC auto-populate). Served by the bridge at GET /api/channel_catalog. Channel ids must mirror frontend/js/eca-encoder.js and frontend/bridge/wb_eca.py CH enum.",
